sources.title: Agenten Kennen Keine Tranen
sources.description: This feature was shot in the midst of some of Europe's most stunning scenery. The story focuses on the efforts of an espionage agent, played by Italian heartthrob Fabio Testi, to secure a uranium shipment that has been targeted by an enemy power. Watch on RetroFlix:  https://retroflix.org/agenten-kennen-keine-tranen-1978/
